title: 196: Were the Twenties the Best Years of Our Lives? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 196
description:
The twenties were a perilous time, and we aren't referring to the Roaring Twenties. R&L dive into some nostalgia as they recount life when they were in their twenties, ponder whether or not ignorance truly is bliss, and more on this episode of Ear Biscuits!
